GEORGE NEWS - The Garden Route District Municipality is hostING an Informal Food Traders Workshop in collaboration with George Municipality on Monday 25 November from 09:00 until 11:00 at the Thembalethu Thusong Centre in Thembalethu, George.

This educational session is designed to empower individuals who own, operate, or work in informal food premises.


> The workshop will provide essential information on the legal requirements for running a spaza shop.


Along with insights from expert speakers on key topics such as:

- Health & Hygiene;
- Fire Safety;
- Building Plan Compliance;
- Waste Management;
- Other important aspects related to operating informal food businesses.

For more information about the event, please contact Jessica Erasmus on 044 803 1522 or WhatsApp 081 346 3118.

